							The App is designed to promote youth wellbeing and mental health literacy. It provides curated suggestions of films, series, books and other media related to youth and mental health, general information on psychological wellbeing, and a private chat feature for informational guidance, clarification of doubts and sharing of opinions about the content.
						</p>
						<p class="mb-4">
							MÔÇES does not provide psychotherapy, psychological assessment, crisis intervention or any clinical services through the App. The chat is intended exclusively for general informational purposes and does not constitute psychological, medical, legal or emergency advice. In an emergency, users should contact the relevant emergency services.
						</p>
						<p>
							The App is intended for individuals aged 12 to 18. Use of the App is subject to the Terms &amp; Conditions available within the App.
						</p>
